text.textblock: Antidrug Program for Personnel Engaged in Specific Aviation Activities

summary.textblock: This document corrects an error to the Final Rule, on ``Antidrug Program for Personnel Engaged in Specific Aviation Activities'', which was published on Thursday, December 23, 1993 (58 FR 68198). The Amendment No. was omitted.

further.textblock: Carol Keenan, Office of Aviation Medicine, Drug Abatement Division (AAM-800), Federal Aviation Administration, 400 Seventh Street, SW., Washington, DC 20590, telephone (202) 366-6710.

supplem.textblock: FR Doc. 93-30930, which was published on December 23, 1993, (58 FR 68198), in the Heading next to the ``Docket No. 25148'', please insert ``Amendment No. 121-235''.
